Emre Can on whether he'll be at Liverpool next season: &ldquo;Why do you ask me this? Really, I concentrate on this season and let my agent handle all the rest.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Emre Can on signing an agreement with another club from January: &quot;Yes I could, but tomorrow I could also sign for Liverpool. We&rsquo;ll see.&rdquo;

Chris Hughton: &quot;Everybody talks about Manchester City at the moment and rightly so as they've done it from day one and haven't lost this season but Liverpool are in Manchester City form.&quot;<br />
<br />
Hughton: &quot;If we look at all the offensive qualities at Manchester City, you have to look at Liverpool as well - the players that are scoring goals and the opportunities they have, which makes them very dangerous opposition.&quot;

Mohamed Salah is a transfer target for Real Madrid, according to Egypt coach Hector Cuper.<br />
<br />
Cuper: &ldquo;I&rsquo;ve received confirmed news revealing Real Madrid&rsquo;s interest in Salah, but let&rsquo;s not rush things. To me, he is in an amazing position right now.&rdquo;
